## Section pipeline

```
WordPress ACF REST
  └─ acf_fc_layout: "audience_promo_card"         ← snake_case string from WP
       │
       ▼
src/lib/acf/normalize-page-sections.ts
  └─ PAGE_SECTION_ACF_LAYOUTS whitelist (must contain the key)
  └─ isKnownPageSectionLayout() type guard
  └─ mapKnownPageSectionLayout() switch → typed AnySectionT
  └─ field-mappers: asString, asHtml, asImage, asLink, mapCtaRepeater, etc.
       │
       ▼
src/lib/acf/enrich-sections.ts  (async second pass, server-side)
  └─ fills: testimonial items, showcase grid service cards,
            blog/case-study paginated lists, CF7 form definitions
       │
       ▼
src/lib/acf/section-registry.ts
  └─ sectionRegistry["audience_promo_card"] → AudiencePromoCardSectionLazy
  └─ getSectionKey(type) type guard: `type in sectionRegistry`
       │
       ▼
src/components/sections/SectionRenderer.tsx
  └─ switch(section.type) — exhaustive, assertNever(section) at default
  └─ <sectionRegistry.audience_promo_card section={section} lang={lang} />
       │
       ▼
src/components/sections/audience-promo-card/index.tsx
  └─ Props: { section: AudiencePromoCardSectionT; lang: Locale }
```

**Every layer must use the identical layout key.** A mismatch at any step silently drops the section.

