## Naming conventions

| Layer                        | Convention                         |
| ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `acf_fc_layout` (WordPress)  | `snake_case`                       |
| `PAGE_SECTION_ACF_LAYOUTS`   | `snake_case`                       |
| `AnySectionT["type"]`        | `snake_case`                       |
| `sectionRegistry` key        | `snake_case`                       |
| `SectionRenderer` case       | `snake_case`                       |
| Component folder             | `kebab-case` (direct 1:1 mapping)  |
| TypeScript type              | `PascalCase` + `SectionT` suffix   |
| Component export name        | `PascalCase` + `Section` suffix    |

Example: `audience_promo_card` → folder `audience-promo-card/` → type `AudiencePromoCardSectionT` → export `AudiencePromoCardSection`.

