## Checklist for a new section

1. Add discriminated union type to `src/types/sections.ts` + add to `AnySectionT`.
2. Add `layout_key: true` to `PAGE_SECTION_ACF_LAYOUTS` in `normalize-page-sections.ts`.
3. Add `case "layout_key":` to `mapKnownPageSectionLayout()` switch.
4. Add dynamic import + registry entry in `section-registry.ts`.
5. Add `case "layout_key":` to `SectionRenderer.tsx` switch.
6. Create `src/components/sections/<kebab-layout-name>/index.tsx`.
7. Add layout to `acf-import-bundle.json` (under `group_omb_page_builder`) with field keys `field_omb_<layout>_*`.
8. Update `ai-context.md` section registry key list.
9. Run `npm run build` to catch assertNever compile errors.

