## GSAP Section Pattern (3-file)

Use this when a section requires client-side scroll animation via useGSAP.

File structure:
  [kebab-layout-key]/
    index.tsx   → React Server Component, dynamically imports lazy.tsx, passes section + lang props
    shell.tsx   → layout/markup only, no animation, accepts same props
    lazy.tsx    → "use client", imports shell, runs useGSAP for reveal logic

Reference implementations: how-it-works-steps/, scrolling-ticker/

Default to single index.tsx unless GSAP is explicitly required.
